{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2e7d2e4d13","title":"金门单日打炮双日不打炮","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"03e8295d8d","index":0,"year":1958,"month":10,"day":31,"articleId":"2e7d2e4d13"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji40","name":"毛泽东全集第40卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/40-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji40":{"comments":[{"id":"72716fdaef","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"2e7d2e4d13","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"恩来，即周恩来。陈毅，当时任国务院副总理兼外交部部长。克诚，即黄克诚，当时任中共中央军委秘书长、国防部副部长、中国人民解放军总参谋长。"},{"id":"b8e39c9a4c","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"2e7d2e4d13","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"从1958年10月上旬开始，中共中央军委令福建前线人民解放军采取打打停停的方式炮击金门。10月25日，国防部又宣布：“逢双日不打金门的飞机场、料罗湾的码头、海滩和船只。"}],"contents":[{"id":"9240c52d3b","type":"title","text":"金门单日打炮双日不打炮","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"2e7d2e4d13"},{"id":"72716fdaef","type":"paragraph","text":"恩来、陈毅、克诚同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"2e7d2e4d13"},{"id":"b8e39c9a4c","type":"paragraph","text":"应将逢双日不打的地方加以推广，就是说，逢双日一律不打炮，使蒋军可以出来活动，晒晒太阳，以利持久。只在单日略为打一点炮。由内部通知福建实行，暂不再发声明。待有必要，再考虑发一声明。此事，请你们商量的定","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"2e7d2e4d13"},{"id":"069a3863bd","type":"paragraph","text":"我今日下午南下。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"2e7d2e4d13"},{"id":"05e191f71b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"2e7d2e4d13"},{"id":"be240dde0e","type":"paragraph","text":"十月三十一日上午二时","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"2e7d2e4d13"}],"page":{"id":"7c52dff9bc","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"2e7d2e4d13","start":340,"end":340}}}},"__N_S